“Thank you, my dear, for this warning.

2510
02:18:17,005 --> 02:18:22,422
I have plans that will keep him absent
quite constantly for the future.”

2511
02:18:22,422 --> 02:18:25,105
And then they spoke less flightily.

2512
02:18:25,105 --> 02:18:28,292
“I always knew,” said the lady,
“that you had found a treasure

2513
02:18:28,292 --> 02:18:29,467
when that man came.”

2514
02:18:29,467 --> 02:18:30,572
The Judge laughed.

2515
02:18:30,572 --> 02:18:34,464
“When it dawned on me,”
