2524
02:18:53,623 --> 02:18:58,300
“But his action regarding the man they
call Steve has made me feel easy.”

2525
02:18:58,300 --> 02:19:02,120
And then it came out that the Virginian
was supposed to have discovered in some

2526
02:19:02,120 --> 02:19:07,445
way that Steve had fallen from the grace
of that particular honesty which

2527
02:19:07,445 --> 02:19:10,651
respects another man’s cattle.

2528
02:19:10,651 --> 02:19:13,179
