2532
02:19:26,689 --> 02:19:28,601
brand of another owner.

2533
02:19:28,601 --> 02:19:33,150
This industry was taking root in Cattle
Land, and of those who practised it,

2534
02:19:33,150 --> 02:19:35,167
some were beginning to be suspected.

2535
02:19:35,167 --> 02:19:38,072
Steve was not quite fully suspected yet.

2536
02:19:38,072 --> 02:19:42,831
But that the Virginian had parted company
with him was definitely known.

2537
02:19:42,831 --> 02:19:44,780
And neither man would talk about it.

2538
02:19:44,780 --> 02:19:50,214
There was the further news that the Bear
Creek schoolhouse at length stood

2539
02:19:50,214 --> 02:19:55,064
complete, floor, walls,
and roof; and that a lady from

2540
02:19:55,064 --> 02:19:59,864
Bennington, Vermont,
a friend of Mrs. Balaam’s,

2541
02:19:59,864 --> 02:20:03,772
had quite suddenly decided that she
would try her hand at

2542
02:20:03,772 --> 02:20:06,457
instructing the new generation.

2543
02:20:06,457 --> 02:20:11,729
The Judge and Mrs. Henry knew this
because Mrs. Balaam had told them of her

2544
02:20:11,729 --> 02:20:15,649
disappointment that she would be absent
from the ranch on Butte Creek when her

2545
02:20:15,649 --> 02:20:19,295
friend arrived, and therefore
unable to entertain her.

2546
02:20:19,295 --> 02:20:23,946
The friend’s decision had been quite
