2674
02:28:32,845 --> 02:28:34,606
much comfort and strengthening.

2675
02:28:34,606 --> 02:28:36,024
“Never!”

2676
02:28:36,024 --> 02:28:38,860
said the old lady, “especially if
you can’t love him.”

2677
02:28:38,860 --> 02:28:42,871
“I do like him,” said Molly;
“and he is very kind.”

2678
02:28:42,871 --> 02:28:44,531
“Never!”

2679
02:28:44,531 --> 02:28:45,465
said the old lady again.

2680
02:28:45,465 --> 02:28:50,196
“When I die, you’ll have something⁠—and
