2682
02:28:55,216 --> 02:28:59,889
And then one winter afternoon,
two years later, came the last straw.

2683
02:28:59,889 --> 02:29:02,093
The front door of the old house had shut.

2684
02:29:02,093 --> 02:29:04,978
Out of it had stepped
the persistent suitor.

2685
02:29:04,978 --> 02:29:05,618
Mrs.

2686
02:29:05,618 --> 02:29:10,453
Flynt watched him drive away
