2689
02:29:16,335 --> 02:29:18,332
posted herself for observation.

2690
02:29:18,332 --> 02:29:23,124
Inside the old house a door had also shut.

2691
02:29:23,124 --> 02:29:25,924
This was the door of Molly’s own room.

2692
02:29:25,924 --> 02:29:29,034
And there she sat, in floods of tears.

2693
02:29:29,034 --> 02:29:33,696
For she could not bear to hurt a man who
loved her with all the power of love

2694
02:29:33,696 --> 02:29:35,216
that was in him.

2695
02:29:35,216 --> 02:29:38,936
It was about twilight when her door
opened, and an elderly

2696
02:29:38,936 --> 02:29:40,995
lady came softly in.

2697
02:29:40,995 --> 02:29:44,137
“My dear,” she ventured,
