2700
02:29:48,896 --> 02:29:51,259
The next day Miss Wood
had become very hard.

2701
02:29:51,259 --> 02:29:55,240
In three weeks she had accepted the
position on Bear Creek.

2702
02:29:55,240 --> 02:29:58,173
In two months she started,
heart-heavy, but with a

2703
02:29:58,173 --> 02:29:59,920
spirit craving the unknown.

