ground to the swing of it.

2722
02:31:09,296 --> 02:31:18,295
By the levels of Bear Creek that reach
like inlets among the promontories of

2723
02:31:18,295 --> 02:31:23,379
the lonely hills, they came upon the
schoolhouse, roofed and ready for the

2724
02:31:23,379 --> 02:31:25,733
first native Wyoming crop.

2725
02:31:25,733 --> 02:31:29,819
It symbolized the dawn of a neighborhood,
and it brought a change

2726
02:31:29,819 --> 02:31:32,076
into the wilderness air.

2727
02:31:32,076 --> 02:31:35,837
The feel of it struck cold upon the free
spirits of the cowpunchers,

2728
02:31:35,837 --> 02:31:39,202
and they told each other that,
what with women and children and wire

2729
02:31:39,202 --> 02:31:43,213
fences, this country would not long be
a country for men.

